* [`d_3`] = [`[$d3]`] [`\textrm{m}`]

* [`P`] = [`[$f]`] [`\textrm{kN/m}`]

Determine the maximum shear force and the maximum bending moment of the beam shown above.

 
[`V_{Max}`] = [_____]{$Vmax} [`\textrm{kN}`]


[`M_{Max}`] = [_____]{$Mc} [`\textrm{kN-m}`]
  

